  Name: Help Board
  Icon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 4521359cb9c97184d8b5666e2e59ad0d, type: 3}
  HasInteraction: 0
  interactionType: 3
  Greeting: Marshal (11 Labs)
  Day1Dialog:
  - "HOW TO PLAY\n\u25AC Move with WASD\n\u25AC Talk to characters with F (interaction
    bubble required)\n\u25AC \"!\" marks a character with today\u2019s task\n\u25AC
    You can complete ONE task per day\n\nPress F for more \u2192"
  - "TASKS & EFFECTS\n\u25AC Infirmary \u2192 Morale \u2191 (uses Bandages)\n\u25AC
    Armoury \u2192 Weapons \u2191 (uses Iron)\n\u25AC Repairs \u2192 Structure \u2191\n\u25AC
    Cat Search \u2192 Cat chance \u2191\n\u25AC Stat gain depends on materials spent\n\nPress
    F for more \u2192"
  - "RESOURCES\n\u25AC Search crates to find materials\n\u25AC Iron \u2192 Armoury\n\u25AC
    Bandages \u2192 Infirmary\n\nPress F for more \u2192"
  - "TIME & DANGER\n\u25AC Time pauses during dialogue\n\u25AC Red circles = incoming
    cannon fire\n\u25AC Getting hit:\n\t\u25AC ends the day\n\t\u25AC loses all progress\n\t\u25AC
    applies \u201320% to all stats\n\nPress F for more \u2192"
  - "FAILURE\n\u25AC If Morale, Weapons, or Structure reach 0% \u2192 Game Over\n\u25AC
    Cat stat does not cause failure#\n\nPress F for more \u2192"
